reviewText: I love all of sisbro movies...These sister and brother have a great talent in filming, editing, composing and acting, but the biggest treat in these movies is the sense of humur. it is so fun to watch.

Bearly Alike is cute, and educational movie. It seems to be meant an audience around 5-12yo. It is good, even that adults like it too. It is a short movie, but that is good for kids. The wildlife video has really cool shots!
